
Overview of noun hiccough

The noun hiccough has 1 sense (no senses from tagged texts)
                                      
1. hiccup, hiccough, singultus -- ((usually plural) the state of having reflex spasms of the diaphragm accompanied by a rapid closure of the glottis producing an audible sound; sometimes a symptom of indigestion; "how do you cure the hiccups?")

